{"tid":2213112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後唔L去百佳惠康買嘢！","createTime":"2020-09-22T09:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T11:40:10.000Z","uid":253354,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34af1d1bd2b5117e86ad197b48c5fc2613b637b9","tid":2213112,"uid":253354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/526918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F526918&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=44137b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/526918</a><br />\n<br />\n保就業計劃｜百佳10月向基層發放4000萬現金食物券　惠康派8000萬<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情打擊下，百業蕭條。百佳超級市場今日（22日）表示，向政府申請第二期保就業計劃，所遞交惠及弱勢社群的建議書亦已獲得接納，10月起將向低收入家庭、長者及傷殘人士發放每人200元的現金食物券，預計受惠人數逾20萬。現金食物券毋需申請，20間社福機構將評估其服務對象的需要發放現金食物券。<br />\n<br />\n惠康方面，計劃與百佳相似，未來10個月將派發200萬張現金劵及餐劵予最有需要的人士，總值超過8,000萬元。"},{"pid":"412682a345f1cc83853c99684559f459a8aac683","tid":2213112,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫下班窮撚都好應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9201ce50dcd005761868eef0f2f1364dc5a68456","tid":2213112,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"有時一路行超市一路上網check價<br />\nhktv仲平"},{"pid":"8a8678b44800b4b80d2f7271d71b298254a2bb71","tid":2213112,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬<